text:
Hello Mr. Byrne,

I hope you are doing well. I'm currently beginning the setup of my next FLIP fluid project and should hopefully have a start to the fluid sometime within the next week or two. I've attached the link to the reference below. I'm also going to try speaking to my thesis advisor about the Amtrak (Snow) train sequence tomorrow and see if they can accept that as a possibility for my thesis. If you have any other suggestions in the meantime, please let me know.

<https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=fxFA9y5Hz6A>
